1.Initialize Nest.js Project

npx @nestjs/cli new notification-preferences-api
cd notification-preferences-api

2.Install Dependencies

npm install mongoose @nestjs/mongoose class-validator class-transformer
npm install @nestjs/swagger swagger-ui-express
npm install --save-dev jest @nestjs/testing

Setup MongoDB

Use a local instance or a cloud-based service like MongoDB Atlas.
Define the connection in app.module.ts using MongooseModule.forRoot().
Serverless Deployment Configuration

Add Vercel or AWS Lambda configuration files.
